Install motion pi:
  sudo apt-get install motion
  
Install ffmpeg, for audio and video streaming:
  sudo apt-get install ffmpeg
  
in /etc/motion/motion.conf (nano /etc/motion/motion.conf) change these entries to the ones below:
  webcam_localhost off
  control_localhost off
  width 640
  height 640
 
Start motion pi with the command:
  motion -n
  
 If you get any errors try changing the ports that video streaming is on. It is by default 8081
